{"hd6a3fca0gbe7eg4a3dg8239gbdf059b85027": ["*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadFF1_Dead.html", "33056b4d-7e3a-8790-adee-bf3103082f5d"], "ha8f4ada2ge413g484agb197gfc72bcced50f": ["*The corpse regards you lifelessly.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadFF1_Dead.html", "d1ef28de-56a0-8ba6-fe9f-c57ef02e9a07"], "hb7c3cb5dg2524g437fgb145g953e5685737a": ["Who are you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadFF1_Dead.html", "7ebd85ed-a397-3097-5bbe-73b8cce6782b"], "h230fbb9egf31fg4376ga1a1g925439530950": ["... Gauntlet... Marilla... Flaming Fist...", "cfd9d50a-14b1-4a25-9d2e-ca626818dcd2", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadFF1_Dead.html", "958b967c-3fd5-59f5-7048-dbe533f6256a"], "h8228c1fagcbd5g4be2gaaeeg041f8bb8eccc": ["Where are you from?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadFF1_Dead.html", "6502d3d1-6417-76a3-a36c-825b10ea059e"], "h38da5dbdg116cg44f9gbe5ag50ee56c4f279": ["... Baldur's Gate...", "cfd9d50a-14b1-4a25-9d2e-ca626818dcd2", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadFF1_Dead.html", "28c08393-a629-7351-fbf6-4d2cc3c92a55"], "h5d1df936gfde4g4730gadd3g5ae3931d964b": ["What happened at the inn?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadFF1_Dead.html", "1c7cf1cd-e4c9-2c15-02ec-64016a58cc7a"], "h9141783bgdfebg400cg8bdbgce9025c54c0e": ["... drow... goblins... had one... in my sights... then darkness...", "cfd9d50a-14b1-4a25-9d2e-ca626818dcd2", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadFF1_Dead.html", "97de7fdc-21dd-5a66-180c-8710aad55654"], "h91537db1gc968g4d0egabe2g2dd389d9a641": ["Why were you at the inn?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadFF1_Dead.html", "1f150175-a864-2543-bb03-fa82b5d2d5e3"], "h9d686889g69aag483dgb2e3gafabb0166c04": ["...guarding... the Grand Duke...", "cfd9d5